Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可疑!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.17,0:01:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把該查的東西查完後 趕快撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 已經沒事嘍 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊毀的敵機裡沒有人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.47,0:01:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無人的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就說是遠距離遙控吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.97,0:01:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們似乎落入圈套了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他剛剛說中「圈套」…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把ADM的情報 顯示出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 船長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是一盤散沙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.97,0:02:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部隊都在交戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前無法詳細匯報
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.97,0:02:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於是在隧道內通信的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.37,0:02:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數據也很混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話 梅麗莎他們就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能老實點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是亂動的話 只會讓你更痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼窄的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…已經死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動哦 子彈會射歪的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是 λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好危險 好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再稍微慢一點發動的話 就死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 敵人的反應有沒有什麼異常?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和預定一樣 正混亂著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯 繼續監視和阻礙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射擊~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz7 向全部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現正在0211 與敵AS交戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人是Venom
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在將把敵人誘導到0112
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有部隊能配合從東面繞過來夾擊他?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本部向Uruz7
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐標有錯誤 再確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在位置是0211…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我傳送正確的坐標Uruz7
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz7向本部 聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在Uruz7 將試著向0112 移動…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…聽得見麼 Uruz7
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Uruz6 現正在與敵AS交戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是格鬥式的Shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先想辦法繞行至0314那裡來擊毀它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向Uruz6 能確定在0216里的Uruz7嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 和預定一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果讓你們現在恢復的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊的生意也就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們老大的抱怨來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Ogma1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁諾上尉 現場的資料連接很混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:06:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是隧道複雜結構的緣故 上校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因漏水和火災的緣故 發生了預料外的空電干擾…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快改善!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最優先!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.85,0:06:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再信任ADM(輔助決策系統)的情報了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切換戰鬥管制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用手動嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就用鉛筆和口傳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不盡快掌握狀況的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…就要全軍覆沒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了嗎「掙扎的話會更痛的」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事…簡直就像…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:07:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有的…徹底的…絕望…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開槍!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要追嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 要優先撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引導人質 別忘了搜他們身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Threatening Terrorist
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混在了人質裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是目的又是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 但如果只是為了殺我們的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要幾個一磅的炸彈就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是為了殺掉我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是在測試我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像被蜘蛛網纏住似的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法搬 就留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz2向全部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭到敵戰鬥員的襲擊 Ruby隊受損傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…死者三人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始Uruz2 將把Topaz隊和人質引導至0216
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FCS(火器控制系統)預測為BK-5456
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有三名死者!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始傳送操作程序 開始解讀暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:08:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話 我將會是第4個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:09:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz6 正在0216與敵人交戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被敵人搶先了 請幫我誘導…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.51,0:09:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本部向Uruz6
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣直接向0316移動 那裡應該沒有敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們就是從那裡來的!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 那麼向0114走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 拜託了哦 老大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz2向本部 現在位於0215
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始把人質向0314移動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡應該沒有敵人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 不過要注意 現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 快退
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz2向本部 已經被敵人搶先埋伏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引導困難 讓人質與Topaz隊一起先逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給與坐標
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向Uruz2 敵人是從0315方向來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 慢慢從相反方向撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz2 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 這是沒理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:10:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這裡的行動 都被敵人預知了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們的通信 是不可能被敵人攔截的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技術上講應該是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…能聽到嗎 請再次重新引導…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 又為什麼…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎 Uruz2放棄護送人質
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並要慢慢撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有Uruz7 根據報道 在向0312移動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz7麼 機名好像是叫Arblest吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 乖乖變成我的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經按照說你說的 去刺探了他們一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼處理他們?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要的話 我可以把他們全殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:10:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管他們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 感覺怎樣啊 Mithril的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 熟練度還算可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過人太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了幾個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才3個男人 雖然有個難纏的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有人礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我可以回家了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濺上了血 令我很噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想沖個澡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Uruz7 躲過敵人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在位置是0312點 現在前去支援Uruz2
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糾正 被敵人發現了 但是好奇怪 這簡直就像..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Uruz6 又被敵人給埋伏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣這也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz9向本部 這邊的撤退點也被敵人埋伏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.99,0:12:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話 會全軍覆滅的!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的沒用的 不管逃到哪裡都是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們為了這天 可是花了很多功夫準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯…情報是洩漏了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…但是這該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果無法引導並管制他們的話 他們就無法戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 只能放棄一切管制手段了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎並非是要讓他們獨立行動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我們要反過來利用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得作戰會議時的對話嗎 少校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果大家還能記住的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一場賭博
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 究竟要走哪邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果按本部的指示的話 是往右邊 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本部向全體命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在給與 最優先的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得作戰會議時 托尼說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托尼的…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說以後再討論的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討論?那是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是 古雷特人的故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指古雷特人都是騙子的悖論吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼話題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 應該沒什麼值得在意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正他們還是會繼續對話的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是什麼都做不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼Uruz9 在那丁字入口 小心向左走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.11,0:13:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向右邊前進 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz9 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要移動了 請站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那邊是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz2 向0112後退 並把敵人引住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz2 向0110前近 把敵人給甩掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz2 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz6 在原地待機 盡量把敵人給壓在原地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.62,0:14:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz6 馬上離開原地 想辦法把敵人給甩掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz6 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz9 向坑道裡面前進
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz9 給我撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 跑啊 跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 Uruz2 向0312前進
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz6 在原地別動 讓敵人過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 佯攻 並把敵人給引住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz9 向03方面前進
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz7 從那個方向回來 繞到02路線去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來向0405出發
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.44,0:15:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz7 瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校 敵人的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是Arblest
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉芳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事 我現在很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對付那種小嘍囉 你想玩到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要正式開場了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點解決掉 到我這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是103正在指示的地方 待機中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人什麼時候會來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是在這裡沒錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也是 沒一個人過來 這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們嘰嘰喳喳的好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們只要按照指示行動就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的行動 我們是一清二楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就耐心的在那裡等獵物來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz6 從那裡向東北逃 准許你任意與敵人交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz6 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz2 就那樣別動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是向0405的移動…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz2 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz9 …
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這前後有矛盾…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是…反過來被他們利用了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用完全相反的命令!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能呢 能這樣做的人是不存…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方只有一架過熱的Arblest
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上去包圍住踩扁它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這被圍之鼠 給完全抓住!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡 做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!? 怎麼?Arblest在哪裡啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!? 啊咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獵物入網了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊 這簡直就是魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總部向全體 聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古雷特人的故事 就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任意開火! 把敵人殲滅掉!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:18:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人!騙人!騙人!　這算是什麼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老鼠反而是我這邊啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮彈對它沒用啊! 這就是那個λ-Driver嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是 宗介你能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.39,0:18:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遲鈍太遲鈍 實在是太遲鈍了!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 你還不能使用嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.79,0:18:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不能運用自如
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.79,0:18:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為這樣讓我上當了? 沒這麼容易
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真讓我失望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那麼一點性能的話 就根本用不著抓你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裡 把你們給全部解決…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告 機器過熱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:18:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 撤回前言! 我按…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可一點都不覺得不甘心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都不覺得不甘心啊 給我記住!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中止戰鬥! 全隊撤退!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複! 全體撤退!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0405發生爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生大規模的漏水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去大部分的通信!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法與友軍取得聯繫…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 M-9是水路兩用的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進水 也是預想中的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Uruz8 總部能聽的到麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現正在布鲁諾的房間 不過來遲了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就是他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是得救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著嗎 庫魯茲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 竟然有內奸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Mithril裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 早上不是有個拿著傳信器的傢伙麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個情報部的叫布魯諾的混蛋 好像就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是他啊 可惡! 害得我們好慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得要讓那傢伙好好的還這份債啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz2向總部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AS隊 全部健全 現在向集合點出發
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 我會派直升機去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是撿回一條命啊 泰莎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝 上校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後為止 都要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果…捕捉Arblest還是失敗了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是毀一個隧道罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 停戰協議
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是討厭那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不知道他 到底在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我們就按老師的吩咐去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 就再忍忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.59,0:21:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.99,0:21:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}きっと君は今日の日も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}你今天一定也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}真っ直ぐ明日を見てる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}直視著明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}風が吹くあの丘に咲いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}彷彿在那微風吹過的山丘上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}向日葵のように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}綻放的向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.46,0:22:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}どんなに遠く離れていても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.46,0:22:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}即使相離再遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}この歌声が君に届くように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}也要把這歌聲傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.47,0:22:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}涙がずっと止まらない夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.47,0:22:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}在這滿臉淚痕的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}君の窓を照らす月になりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}希望成為照亮你窗前的月光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:23:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}また必ず会えると そう思うから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:23:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}一定會再相見的 我這麼相信著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.39,0:23:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛徒逃到了罪惡的黑手黨那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.59,0:23:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地中海的微風和寂靜的港灣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.79,0:23:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預料之外的戲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.39,0:23:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及那漆黑的突擊者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.69,0:23:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 美麗的西西里島
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.40,0:23:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是逃到天涯海角 我也要抓住你!
